No, no. That's not it.

1694
01:26:36,822 --> 01:26:38,240
Was it in French?

1695
01:26:38,407 --> 01:26:40,284
I'll know it when I hear it.

1696
01:27:05,267 --> 01:27:08,228
Yes. That was it.

1697
01:27:08,395 --> 01:27:09,479
That's right.

1698
01:27:09,646 --> 01:27:12,482
We made it up.
