1784
01:31:16,643 --> 01:31:17,644
Committee of the Five?

1785
01:31:18,145 --> 01:31:19,563
Committee for a Sound Dollar.

1786
01:31:22,900 --> 01:31:25,152
The nation needs your leadership.

1787
01:31:25,319 --> 01:31:27,154
