01:31:35,120 --> 01:31:36,538
This is very exciting.

1791
01:31:37,289 --> 01:31:40,167
I'll choose the event.
I'm most comfortable...

1792
01:31:40,334 --> 01:31:42,419
speaking with the veterans
Bill Meekins knew...

1793
