1886
01:36:31,500 --> 01:36:33,001
- No, sir, never at your expense.
- No, God. No, no, sir.

1887
01:36:33,168 --> 01:36:34,169
- Never at your expense, please.
- No, sir.

1888
01:36:34,378 --> 01:36:36,463
There's a lot of people I care about
