1896
01:36:58,610 --> 01:36:59,820
Yes?

1897
01:37:02,155 --> 01:37:04,616
I hope this son-of-a-bitch thing works.

1898
01:37:06,285 --> 01:37:07,369
Or else we're fucked.

1899
01:37:08,453 --> 01:37:10,873
<i>Welcome to the 14th annual gala...</i>

1900
